title: Schumann - The Symphonies - Karajan, BPO
description:
Schumann: The Four Symphonies.

NOTE: A few months ago I uploaded the Karajan set of the Schumann Symphonies, not realizing that due to a scratch on the first disc, the Second Symphony contained audio distortions. This new upload is a completely clean copy!

Karajan recorded these four symphonies in the late 1960s and the complete set was released by DG in 1972.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
